Foretokens
Artist: Barbara McCarren
2000

Foretokens is a series of cast bronze amulets attached to sculptural bases placed at every tee at the Rancho Del Pueblo Golf Course. The idea of icons of power (lucky tokens) affecting fate is a universal concept, inspired the artist to create nine bronze talismans for the nine-hole golf course including: a lucky penny, a horseshoe, a wishbone, a four-leaf clover, a hand milagro, a scarab, a rabbit’s foot, a bat, and a Zuni bear fetish.


    
        
