Explore time through the movement of this suspended sculpture that breathes, ripples and reacts to passengers while maintaining its abacus-like counting pattern.  As each row completes its count, the movement is marked by the closing of a single element.  The counting then resumes until the total array closes; time stands still until the counting begins again. 


    
        
