Animal Spiral and Butterfly Dreams
Artist: Therese May
1991 and 1993


The two 14-foot square quilts originally created for the San Jose Convention Center moved to a new home at Seven Trees Community Center (2013). Both quilts speak to the theme of transformation.  Butterfly Dreams, presents a universal symbol of transformation.  Animal Spiral focuses on the journey home in a spiral with a pathway to the center.

    
        
